title: Patriotic dog leash
description: The deluxe patriotic dog leash has a fun United States flag design with stars, stripes along with the colors red, white and blue. Leash is made with sturdy nylon and has a metal latch that can be attached to a collar. Has a looped handle for a secure hold. Leash measures 47", leash clip measures 3 1/4". Total length is 50 1/4" from end to end. The total width is almost 3/4".

title: Patriotic dog collar
description: Show off you and your pet's American pride with this patriotic dog collar. Has a fun red, white and blue design that reflects the look of the United States flag. Collar is made with sturdy nylon and has a plastic side squeeze latch. Has a metal hook so leashes can easily clip on. Comes packaged on a tie card with hanging hole. Collar is adjustable and can expand up to 20" from end to end. Collar is appoximately 3/4" wide.

title: Patriotic Auto Flag
description: Great for Independence Day, Memorial Day or all year long - this patriotic auto flag easily mounts to car windows. Comes packaged loose with a hang tag. Nylon flag measures 19" x 11 1/4". The sturdy plastic window mount is 17 1/2" long.

title: Sandpaper value pack
description: The sandpaper pack is perfect for sanding metal, wood and painted surfaces. Each package comes with 10 sheets of 8" x 10" sandpaper. Sandpaper is medium grit. Great for home or industrial use. Comes packaged in a hanging panel with butterfly hole.

title: Wood handle paint brush set
description: This 3 pack of paint brushes have red painted handles made with contoured wood. Perfect for home or industrial use. Nylon bristles hold paint for a smooth finish. Brushes come in three assorted sizes. These are packaged in a poly bag with header card. Brush sizes are 1/2", 3/4" and 1 7/8".
